QuestData.Title: A Score to Settle
QuestData.Description: Utgarde's forces are organizing under the advisory of Prince Keleseth, a san'layn ambassador of the Scourge.$B$BWe cannot allow the vrykul to benefit from his counsel any further. Silence him.
QuestData.LogDescription: Dark Ranger Marrah wants you to slay Prince Keleseth inside Utgarde Keep.
QuestData.RewardText: Revenge feels good. To think that this is but a taste of what's to come.$B$BArthas will get what he deserves soon enough.
